data.description: Looking to live your luxury, coastal dreams? Look no further than this completely custom 2022 Murrell Build, full of upgrades upon upgrades all on 0.79 acres in the prestigious Osprey Cove. All 3010 square feet are thoughtfully designed with the owners in mind. The split floorplan boasts 5 bedrooms and 2 and half baths, with four bedrooms being on the first floor and the 5th being upstairs. The 5th is large and can be utilized as a bedroom or bonus space. With it's well-designed plan and choice of upgrades, this home is perfect for whomever is looking to have a luxury but laid back interior and a spacious outdoor living area and yard. Gas front porch lanterns, gas fireplace, oversized master shower, spacious pantry, large windows, retractable screens out back to allow for open air or closed lanai, heated/chilled pool.. too many upgrades to name. With this home, the photos speak for themselves. Come live the life in this stunning home in your favorite Coastal Georgia golf community! 2.875% assumable VA loan option
